title: UGREEN Micro USB Fast Charger Cable USB to Micro B Data Lead Compatible with Samsung A10 S7 S6 Edge J7 J6 J5 J4 Plus J3…
html: UGREEN Micro USB Fast Charger Cable USB to Micro B Data Lead Compatible with Samsung A10 S7 S6 Edge J7 J6 J5 J4 Plus J3…
description: 18W Fast Charge & Speedy Syncing: UGREEN Micro USB to USB Cable supports both Quick Charge 2.0/3.0 and Huawei PCF Fast Charge technology and delivers current up to 2.4A and supports 18W max power output(12V/1.5A, 9V/2A, 5V/2.4A), which enables to charge most devices at their full speed. For example, fully charge Samsung Galaxy S7 in 1.5h. Simultaneously supports high-speed data transmission rate up to 480Mbps, transferring 1GB files in minutes. A perfect time-saver for you. Bendable Connection & Fit Snugly: UGREEN USB to Micro USB Charger Cable features a reinforced bendable plug and wire connection design, making the cable anti-stretch and anti-folding as well as strong enough to withstand abuse treatment like hard pull, which allows you to move around freely. No need to worry about bending the cable to make the wire crack or the charging stopped. This flexible design also helps maintain a tight fit on both ends and ensures stable charging and data sync. Build to Last: The combination of high-quality materials and flexible construction design endues more durability to UGREEN Micro USB Fast Charger Lead. Passing 10,000+ bend tests, the exterior double-layer nylon braid jacket provides unrivalled protection to the inner wires. The premium aluminium connectors are anti-corrosion,anti-oxidation and anti overheat. Moreover, the flexible bendable joint design adds more durability and longer lifespan to the charging cable.
